        h2 From Consulting to Connecting  
      p
        i "I studied Computer Science and Business at the University of Pennsylvania. After that, I worked in consulting with Bain & Company in New York.
      p
        i One project I’ve worked on at Facebook that I am incredibly passionate about is internet.org. About 80% of the world’s population lives within range of a 2G or 3G connection, yet over 4 billion people remain unconnected to the internet. As an RPM, I’ve gotten to partner with carriers to find economically sustainable ways to make mobile data more affordable and accessible for the world."
        .quote  -Ashley Yuki, 2013 RPM  
    a.button.style2.down.anchored(href='#four') Next

    //
     Andrew
  section#four.main.style2.right.dark.fullscreen
    .content.box.interviewPage
