        h2 You betcha. 
      p
        i "Fun fact: in my first product review with Mark Zuckerberg (during my 7th week at Facebook), I presented wearing a shirt & tie … and spandex bike shorts. I lost a bet to one of my RPM managers, but Mark thought the outfit was great. The review went well!
      p
        i Jokes aside, I grew up in Canada and studied at the University of Waterloo. After a few great internship experiences, I decided to move to Silicon Valley. As a PM at Facebook, I’ve learned how to feel when a team is operating well and working towards a vision that everyone is bought into."
        br
        .quote  -Andrew Song, 2012 RPM 
    a.button.style2.down.anchored(href='#five') Next

    //
     Henry
  section#five.main.style2.left.dark.fullscreen
